text: Jorge Mosera Sipaco (born 28 May 2002) is an Equatorial Guinean footballer who plays as a defender for Cano Sport Academy and the Equatorial Guinea national team. ==Club career== Mosera moved from Real X Balompié to Cano Sport in January 2019. ==International career== Mosera made his international debut for Equatorial Guinea on 28 July 2019. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Association football defenders Category:Equatoguinean footballers Category:Equatorial Guinea international footballers Category:Equatorial Guinea youth international footballers Category:Cano Sport Academy players Category:Bubi people
